\C[17]Rule Explanation\C[0]Confirm Button: Attack Cancel Button:
Forward Dash

\C[17]Combat Explanation\C[0]Samejima will approach Yui to launch
strikes and grappling moves. Avoid getting too close to Samejima and
evade his approach to land your attacks.

Yui's attacks only have a hitbox \C[17]two squares directly in front
of her\C[0]. When Samejima is two squares in front, time your attacks
well with the confirm button.

If an attack hits, Samejima will \C[17]flash red\C[0] and be blown
significantly backward. Landing five attacks will secure a victory.

Conversely, if Samejima gets too close, you'll be caught in a
grappling move, and if you're grappled three times, it will result in
defeat.

Furthermore, the range of movement is confined \C[17]inside the red
line\C[0].
Now, the match will start after 3 seconds.
Would you like a hint for the conquest?

\c[17]Judo Knowledge\c[0] equipped will give you an advantage in
battle. Try searching for the \c[17]Judo Knowledge\c[0] hidden within
the school.
